```
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Virtual environment
venv/
env/
ENV/

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# Database
*.db
*.sqlite3

# Environment variables
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Logs
logs/
*.log

# Local Docker volumes
data/

# Coverage
htmlcov/
.coverage
.coverage.*
.cache
.pytest_cache/

# Distribution / packaging
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/

# MyPy
.mypy_cache/
.dmypy.json
dmypy.json

# Pyre type checker
.pyre/

# Alembic versions (but keep the directory)
alembic/versions/*.py
!alembic/versions/__init__.py

# Kubernetes secrets (don't commit real secrets)
kubernetes/*.yaml
!kubernetes/*.example.yaml
```